cmpReviews: HireMinds is a great company and has fantastic people. They will push you and keep you on target. Only for serious recruiters who truly feel they have a knack for the industry.If you are a job seeker and are attempting to work with this agency, dont waste your time. They are AWFUL. I have crossed paths with these hacks a few different times in my 12 year career, and each encounter gets more and more woeful. They are beyond unprofessional. They are the epitome of the key word search agencies.I work with a great group of individuals motivated to succeed and work together to secure top talent for Boston area companies.
